### Global Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@requestId = {{ $guid }}
@contentType = application/json

### 1. Get All Suppliers (Pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/suppliers?page=0&size=10
X-Request-ID: {{requestId}}

### 2. Get Supplier by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/suppliers/2
X-Request-ID: {{requestId}}

### Create New Supplier
POST {{baseUrl}}/suppliers
X-Request-ID: {{requestId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "code": "VEND-001",
  "name": "PT. Elektronik Maju Jaya",
  "email": "sales@maju-jaya.com",
  "address": "Kawasan Industri Jababeka Blok C-12"
}

### Validataion Test
POST {{baseUrl}}/suppliers
X-Request-ID: {{requestId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "code": "VEND-002",
  "name2": "PT. Angin Ribut",
  "email": "salesangin-ribut.com",
  "address": "Kawasan Industri Jababeka Blok C-13"
}

### Delete Supplier
DELETE  {{baseUrl}}/suppliers/2
X-Request-ID: {{requestId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}



### 3. Create Purchase Order (Draft)
# Pastikan supplierId 1 sudah ada di database sebelum menjalankan ini
POST {{baseUrl}}/purchase-orders
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
X-Request-ID: {{requestId}}

{
  "supplierId": 2,
  "items": [
    {
      "itemId": 101,
      "quantity": 10,
      "price": 15000.00
    },
    {
      "itemId": 102,
      "quantity": 5,
      "price": 25500.50
    }
  ]
}

### 4. Get Purchase Order by ID
# Ganti ID '1' dengan ID yang didapat dari response POST di atas
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchase-orders/2
X-Request-ID: {{requestId}}

### 5. Create PO with Invalid Supplier (Error Handling Test)
POST {{baseUrl}}/purchase-orders
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
X-Request-ID: {{requestId}}

{
  "supplierId": 9999,
  "items": []
}

### 6. Update status PO
PUT {{baseUrl}}/purchase-orders/update-status/2
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
X-Request-ID: {{requestId}}

{
  "status": "DRAFT"
}